  40:Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h7xx_hal_ltdc.c ****          the LTDC timing, the horizontal and vertical polarity, the pixel clock polarity,
  41:Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h7xx_hal_ltdc.c ****          Data Enable polarity and the LTDC background color value using HAL_LTDC_Init() function
  42:Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h7xx_hal_ltdc.c **** 
