 102:Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h7xx_hal_ltdc.c **** 
 103:Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h7xx_hal_ltdc.c ****      *** Callback registration ***
 104:Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h7xx_hal_ltdc.c ****      =============================================
 105:Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h7xx_hal_ltdc.c ****      [..]
 106:Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h7xx_hal_ltdc.c ****      The compilation define  USE_HAL_LTDC_REGISTER_CALLBACKS when set to 1
 107:Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h7xx_hal_ltdc.c ****      allows the user to configure dynamically the driver callbacks.
 108:Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h7xx_hal_ltdc.c ****      Use function HAL_LTDC_RegisterCallback() to register a callback.
 109:Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h7xx_hal_ltdc.c **** 
 110:Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h7xx_hal_ltdc.c ****     [..]
 111:Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h7xx_hal_ltdc.c ****     Function HAL_LTDC_RegisterCallback() allows to register following callbacks:
 112:Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h7xx_hal_ltdc.c ****       (+) LineEventCallback   : LTDC Line Event Callback.
 113:Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h7xx_hal_ltdc.c ****       (+) ReloadEventCallback : LTDC Reload Event Callback.
 114:Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h7xx_hal_ltdc.c ****       (+) ErrorCallback       : LTDC Error Callback
 115:Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h7xx_hal_ltdc.c ****       (+) MspInitCallback     : LTDC MspInit.
 116:Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h7xx_hal_ltdc.c ****       (+) MspDeInitCallback   : LTDC MspDeInit.
 117:Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h7xx_hal_ltdc.c ****     [..]
 118:Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h7xx_hal_ltdc.c ****     This function takes as parameters the HAL peripheral handle, the callback ID
 119:Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h7xx_hal_ltdc.c ****     and a pointer to the user callback function.
 120:Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h7xx_hal_ltdc.c **** 
 121:Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h7xx_hal_ltdc.c ****     [..]
 122:Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h7xx_hal_ltdc.c ****     Use function HAL_LTDC_UnRegisterCallback() to reset a callback to the default
 123:Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h7xx_hal_ltdc.c ****     weak function.
 124:Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h7xx_hal_ltdc.c ****     HAL_LTDC_UnRegisterCallback() takes as parameters the HAL peripheral handle
 125:Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h7xx_hal_ltdc.c ****     and the callback ID.
 126:Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h7xx_hal_ltdc.c ****     [..]
 127:Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h7xx_hal_ltdc.c ****     This function allows to reset following callbacks:
 128:Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h7xx_hal_ltdc.c ****       (+) LineEventCallback   : LTDC Line Event Callback
 129:Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h7xx_hal_ltdc.c ****       (+) ReloadEventCallback : LTDC Reload Event Callback
 130:Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h7xx_hal_ltdc.c ****       (+) ErrorCallback       : LTDC Error Callback
 131:Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h7xx_hal_ltdc.c ****       (+) MspInitCallback     : LTDC MspInit
 132:Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h7xx_hal_ltdc.c ****       (+) MspDeInitCallback   : LTDC MspDeInit.
 133:Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h7xx_hal_ltdc.c **** 
 134:Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h7xx_hal_ltdc.c ****     [..]
 135:Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h7xx_hal_ltdc.c ****     By default, after the HAL_LTDC_Init and when the state is HAL_LTDC_STATE_RESET
 136:Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h7xx_hal_ltdc.c ****     all callbacks are set to the corresponding weak functions:
 137:Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h7xx_hal_ltdc.c ****     examples HAL_LTDC_LineEventCallback(), HAL_LTDC_ErrorCallback().
 138:Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h7xx_hal_ltdc.c ****     Exception done for MspInit and MspDeInit functions that are
 139:Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h7xx_hal_ltdc.c ****     reset to the legacy weak (surcharged) functions in the HAL_LTDC_Init() and HAL_LTDC_DeInit()
 140:Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h7xx_hal_ltdc.c ****     only when these callbacks are null (not registered beforehand).
 141:Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h7xx_hal_ltdc.c ****     If not, MspInit or MspDeInit are not null, the HAL_LTDC_Init() and HAL_LTDC_DeInit()
 142:Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h7xx_hal_ltdc.c ****     keep and use the user MspInit/MspDeInit callbacks (registered beforehand).
 143:Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h7xx_hal_ltdc.c **** 
 144:Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h7xx_hal_ltdc.c ****     [..]
 145:Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h7xx_hal_ltdc.c ****     Callbacks can be registered/unregistered in HAL_LTDC_STATE_READY state only.
ARM GAS  /var/folders/l4/6w9kflz11csb_6qsyz46nv3c0000gp/T//ccooKEPs.s 			page 4


 146:Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h7xx_hal_ltdc.c ****     Exception done MspInit/MspDeInit that can be registered/unregistered
 147:Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h7xx_hal_ltdc.c ****     in HAL_LTDC_STATE_READY or HAL_LTDC_STATE_RESET state,
 148:Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h7xx_hal_ltdc.c ****     thus registered (user) MspInit/DeInit callbacks can be used during the Init/DeInit.
 149:Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h7xx_hal_ltdc.c ****     In that case first register the MspInit/MspDeInit user callbacks
 150:Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h7xx_hal_ltdc.c ****     using HAL_LTDC_RegisterCallback() before calling HAL_LTDC_DeInit()
 151:Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h7xx_hal_ltdc.c ****     or HAL_LTDC_Init() function.
 152:Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h7xx_hal_ltdc.c **** 
 153:Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h7xx_hal_ltdc.c ****     [..]
 154:Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h7xx_hal_ltdc.c ****     When the compilation define USE_HAL_LTDC_REGISTER_CALLBACKS is set to 0 or
 155:Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h7xx_hal_ltdc.c ****     not defined, the callback registration feature is not available and all callbacks
 156:Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h7xx_hal_ltdc.c ****     are set to the corresponding weak functions.
 157:Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h7xx_hal_ltdc.c **** 
 158:Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h7xx_hal_ltdc.c ****   @endverbatim
 159:Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h7xx_hal_ltdc.c ****   ******************************************************************************
 160:Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h7xx_hal_ltdc.c ****   */
 161:Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h7xx_hal_ltdc.c **** 
